{"tid":1564940,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《信報》引消息：警隊提高 OT 補水上限","createTime":"2019-09-13T03:07:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T03:41:39.000Z","uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"723cfd9bb580ba4731df7a0300ab3fc5ab338fb5","tid":1564940,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T03:07:20.000Z","msg":"《信報》政情專欄「香港脈搏」今天引述消息人士指，前線警員連月應付遊行衝突，逾時開工已成常態，令累積 OT 時間不斷創新高。當局有見及此，只好再次調整津貼制度，把紀律部隊超時工作津貼（DSOA）上限，由 120 小時調高至 150 小時；另外取消用 OT 時數換取補假上限（原本為 180 小時），避免警員逾時上班「爆額」，變成無償開 OT。<br />\n<br />\n「香港脈搏」作者余錦賢引述消息人士，調高DSOA限額有助提振警員士氣，一來前線有「現兜兜」真金白銀到手，二來管理層亦樂見風頭火勢下不會有太多前線同事被迫「清假」，影響警隊動員和部署。然而，由於總督察以上職級，制度上不容許「以錢代假」，故仍有部分高層 OT 以百小時計，當局唯有取消「OT 換補假」累積上限。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%BF%A1%E5%A0%B1-%E5%BC%95%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF-%E8%AD%A6%E9%9A%8A%E6%8F%90%E9%AB%98-ot-%E8%A3%9C%E6%B0%B4%E4%B8%8A%E9%99%90/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E5%25A0%25B1-%25E5%25BC%2595%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%2581%25AF-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%259A%258A%25E6%258F%2590%25E9%25AB%2598-ot-%25E8%25A3%259C%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E4%25B8%258A%25E9%2599%2590%2F&d=m%2FBV6vIUiVByATU953YnmAxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=e8746c03\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E5%25A0%25B1-%25E5%25BC%2595%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%2581%25AF-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%259A%258A%25E6%258F%2590%25E9%25AB%2598-ot-%25E8%25A3%259C%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E4%25B8%258A%25E9%2599%2590%2F&h=fbdbc59a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%BF%A1%E5%A0%B1-%E5%BC%95%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF-%E8%AD%A6%E9%9A%8A%E6%8F%90%E9%AB%98-ot-%E8%A3%9C%E6%B0%B4%E4%B8%8A%E9%99%90/</a>"},{"pid":"571240325b36ca560dadf31df8d14f38997c229a","tid":1564940,"uid":25185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T03:07:30.000Z","msg":"【 突發】和理塞 商場篇 終於出爐!922第一彈約定你<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1563867\" target=\"